title: GDG DevFest 2017 Announced
brief: Seattle Google Developers Group is proud to announce the fifth annual GDG DevFest 2017 which is the biggest Google related event in Seattle carefully crafted by GDG community! The event will take place on **October 7 ** in **Seattle**.
